WEBVTT

00:00:00.280 --> 00:00:04.309
Hey, good morning family! I'm excited to be with you all again today.

00:00:04.310 --> 00:00:15.282
I am going to do another 'Pray with Me'video to motivate yourself to pray. I'll be praying in English and I'll be praying in tongues.

00:00:15.283 --> 00:00:27.123
I believe corporate prayer is important in these last days, even more than ever before. Now is the time we need to pray as a body.

00:00:27.124 --> 00:00:35.716
I believe as we join together in this video, there will be many of you praying for unsaved loved ones and the nation.

00:00:35.717 --> 00:00:48.978
Whatever is on your heart, let's just pray together. I'll be leading the prayer by myself; I'm not going to do it with Lynn Hammond in a split screen.

00:00:48.979 --> 00:00:55.461
I'm just going to do it how I pray every day by myself and seek the Lord.

00:00:55.462 --> 00:01:05.626
I'm letting you into my prayer time and we are just going to pray and seek the Father to see what He has for us.

00:01:05.627 --> 00:01:10.809
I hope this helps you jump into the river in your own personal prayer life.

00:01:10.810 --> 00:01:20.594
I'm not saying I'm the greatest prayer warrior, but the Lord told me to do it, so I'm jumping into this river and let's see where it takes us.

00:01:20.595 --> 00:01:30.686
I always start out by singing a song to the Father. I enter His courts with thanksgiving and praise, and that's what we're going to do right now.

00:01:30.687 --> 00:01:39.227
Father, we just want to say thank you for all that You've done and all that You're going to do.

00:01:39.228 --> 00:01:45.878
Lord, we worship You and thank You for this day. We thank You, Father, for a new day that You've given us.

00:01:45.879 --> 00:01:51.658
This is the day that the Lord has made, and we will rejoice and be glad in it.

00:01:51.659 --> 00:01:59.339
Father, I just want to say thank You for the air that I breathe, for the food that we eat today, and for all that You've provided.

00:01:59.340 --> 00:02:15.999
As we start a new month, I thank You that we're getting ready for September and that You've provided for all the bills for the month of September for every household represented here.

00:02:16.000 --> 00:02:24.425
Whether it is electric, water, gas, phones, or car payments, whatever they have need of, Father, You've provided.

00:02:24.426 --> 00:02:33.990
I thank You, Father, that You are the great provider, the great Jehovah. I want to give You praise and glory.

00:02:33.991 --> 00:02:48.679
I'm just going to sing You a song, Father, and I thank You that You said You inhabit the praises of Your people. We give You praise and we want to worship You today, Father.

00:02:48.680 --> 00:02:57.980
We honor You and thank You, Lord, that You're so real to us and that there is a heavy presence of Your Spirit on us today.

00:02:57.981 --> 00:03:06.017
We invite You into this day, into our homes, our jobs, and our workplaces.

00:03:06.018 --> 00:03:16.642
Holy Spirit, I thank You that You're going with our children to school today and that You protect them.

00:03:16.643 --> 00:03:29.895
No weapon formed against them shall prosper. I plead the blood over our children; no weapon and no devil in hell can come nigh them.

00:03:29.896 --> 00:03:36.321
Not one hair on their heads will be touched by any kind of demonic attack.

00:03:36.322 --> 00:03:49.478
I thank You, Lord, that You are protecting them and that You send Your angels to bear us up in their hands lest we dash our foot against a stone.

00:03:49.479 --> 00:03:57.500
I thank You for Psalm 23 and Psalm 91. I give You praise and glory.

00:03:57.501 --> 00:05:00.758
Father, we say: fill my cup, Lord, I lift it up. Lord, come and quench this thirsting of my soul.

00:05:00.759 --> 00:05:23.022
Bread of Heaven, feed me till I want no more. Fill my cup, fill it up and make me whole.

00:05:23.023 --> 00:06:05.329
It is Jesus. We worship You, Holy Spirit. You are welcome in this place.

00:06:05.330 --> 00:07:26.875
Omnipotent Father of mercy and grace, Thou art welcome in this place.

00:07:26.876 --> 00:07:43.296
Jesus is coming soon, morning or night or noon. Many will meet their doom; trumpets will surely sound.

00:07:43.297 --> 00:08:53.679
All of the dead shall rise, righteous meet in the sky, going where no one dies, Heavenward bound.

00:08:53.680 --> 00:09:35.409
Lord, You're coming so soon. Lord, we're so thirsty and we need a fresh touch today.

00:09:35.410 --> 00:09:56.315
Come and quench this thirsting of my soul. Bread of Heaven, feed me till I want no more.

00:09:56.316 --> 00:11:34.494
Fill my cup, fill it up and make me whole. Amazing Grace, how sweet the sound that saved a wretch like me.

00:11:34.495 --> 00:12:13.629
I once was lost, but now I'm found, was blind but now I see. Through many dangers, toils, and snares, I have already come.

00:12:13.630 --> 00:12:30.759
'Tis grace that brought me safe this far, and grace will lead me home.

00:12:30.760 --> 00:13:06.799
When we've been there ten thousand years, bright shining as the sun, we've no less days to sing God's praise than when we first begun.

00:13:06.800 --> 00:13:22.266
Thank You, Father, that even when we mess up the words, You still inhabit the praises of Your people because it's from our hearts.

00:13:22.267 --> 00:13:30.892
Father, we thank You that if we abide in You and Your words abide in us, we shall ask what we will.

00:13:30.893 --> 00:14:17.278
We lift up all the needs of the people today. If we make much of the blood, the blood makes much of us. What can wash away my sin? Nothing but the blood of Jesus.

00:14:17.279 --> 00:14:54.233
Oh, precious is the flow that makes me white as snow; no other fount I know, nothing but the blood of Jesus.

00:14:54.234 --> 00:16:50.239
The blood that gives me strength from day to day will never lose its power, for it reaches to the highest mountain and flows to the lowest valley.

00:16:50.240 --> 00:17:39.955
Glory to the Lamb! You are glorious and worthy to be praised.

00:17:39.956 --> 00:18:22.874
You're the Lamb upon the throne, and unto You, we lift our voice in praise.

00:18:22.875 --> 00:18:39.823
Father, we thank You for Your hand on this house. We worship You and give You glory right now in Jesus'name.

00:18:39.824 --> 00:19:21.657
Holy Spirit, we invite You now. What is on Your heart for us to pray for today?

00:19:21.658 --> 00:19:37.247
We yield ourselves over to the Holy Spirit and thank You that You become so real to us.

00:19:37.248 --> 00:19:56.527
There are so many needs and things pressing that seem overwhelming, but we thank You, Lord, that You are the peace in the midst of the storm.

00:19:56.528 --> 00:20:19.689
You say, 'Peace, be still,'to all storms. We call peace to every storm in the lives of every individual here today, in marriages and for children.

00:20:19.690 --> 00:20:25.639
We take authority over you, Satan, and we tell you: thus far and no further!

00:20:25.640 --> 00:20:38.257
Get your hands off of God's property. We call those in the storm of life healed, whole, and well in Jesus'name.

00:20:38.258 --> 00:21:01.415
You are the great storm peacemaker; You spoke to the waves and said, 'Peace, be still.'We thank You, Lord, that You're the mighty one, the Creator of everything.

00:21:01.416 --> 00:21:15.137
You created us even in our mothers'wombs. Every cell and every hair on our head was fearfully and wonderfully made.

00:21:15.138 --> 00:21:41.475
I thank You that we go up higher and higher with You in greater glory and greater manifestations of Your presence.

00:21:41.476 --> 00:21:48.751
We want to be at the spout where the glory comes out, going from glory to glory.

00:21:48.752 --> 00:22:10.626
I thank You, Lord, for the manifestations of that glory in our homes. We want to be a vessel that You use in these last days.

00:22:10.627 --> 00:22:18.967
The eyes of the Lord run to and fro throughout the whole earth, looking for a heart whose heart is perfect toward Him.

00:22:18.968 --> 00:22:39.203
Let Your eyes rest upon me today, oh God. Create in me a clean heart, oh God.

00:22:39.204 --> 00:22:45.452
You are the Potter and I am the clay; mold me and make me today.

00:22:45.453 --> 00:23:05.901
We have this treasure in earthen vessels, that the excellency of the power would be of You and not of me.

00:23:05.902 --> 00:23:30.939
Holy Spirit, make me more like Jesus. We are yielded, filled, and controlled by the Holy Spirit today.

00:23:30.940 --> 00:23:43.155
We are at that river of living water flowing out of the throne. We're coming up higher with the fire.

00:23:43.156 --> 00:23:48.158
There are levels of the prophetic and levels of Your presence.

00:23:48.159 --> 00:24:29.482
Father, we yield ourselves to You today so that we would be a light in the darkness and the salt of the earth—the salt that makes people thirsty for You.

00:24:29.483 --> 00:24:40.263
Help us to be the light to somebody today, an answer to prayer in their heart.

00:24:40.264 --> 00:24:54.359
Let Your glory shine on our faces like it did upon Moses. Let our shadow pass by like it did the disciples, so that healing flows.

00:24:54.360 --> 00:25:12.866
Even if they touched the shadow, the glory was pouring out so strong that it would heal them.

00:25:12.867 --> 00:25:25.903
Do it again, Lord! Do it in us; do it in me. Create in us a clean heart, God.

00:25:25.904 --> 00:25:49.976
In these last days, pour out Your Spirit upon us one more time like You did at Azusa Street.

00:25:49.977 --> 00:26:37.922
I thank You, Lord, for the greatest harvest of souls this world has ever seen—a billion-soul harvest that would happen quickly and suddenly in the name of Jesus.

00:26:37.923 --> 00:26:51.328
I call each person watching this video today healed and whole. Nothing is too big for You, Lord.

00:26:51.329 --> 00:27:07.300
I call them blessed, healed, and whole mentally, emotionally, physically, and financially.

00:27:07.301 --> 00:27:22.508
I thank You, Father, for healing power that flows on the inside of them, driving out all sickness and disease.

00:27:22.509 --> 00:27:31.117
It's already done, and we receive it. Faith calls those things that be not as though they were.

00:27:31.118 --> 00:27:44.960
You paid the price for us to walk in healing. Lord, we pray over our finances.

00:27:44.961 --> 00:27:50.362
You said to seek first the kingdom and all these things will be added.

00:27:50.363 --> 00:28:32.940
We seek You today, knowing You know we have every need. We seek You, not for the things, but for You.

00:28:32.941 --> 00:28:38.937
We take the care out of our prayer and cast our cares onto You because You care for us.

00:28:38.938 --> 00:28:44.879
If You care for the lily of the field and the sparrow, how much more do You care for us?

00:28:44.880 --> 00:29:00.011
David said he had never seen the righteous forsaken nor his seed begging bread.

00:29:00.012 --> 00:29:12.319
I thank You that we are the righteousness of God in Christ Jesus.

00:29:12.320 --> 00:29:27.435
As we seek You daily, we will find You. We knock, and the door is opened to us.

00:29:27.436 --> 00:30:03.409
You have prepared a table before us in the presence of our enemies, and we rest in the finished work of Jesus Christ.

00:30:03.410 --> 00:30:40.907
Great is Your faithfulness to us. Morning by morning, new mercies I see; all I have needed Thy hand hath provided.

00:30:40.908 --> 00:31:44.144
Thank You for our unsaved loved ones. We send laborers across their path today.

00:31:44.145 --> 00:32:11.354
Some plant, some water, and some bring forth the increase, but we keep the door open by the blood.

00:32:11.355 --> 00:32:41.397
We call them home in Jesus'name. One last call—wake up! We call them to a fresh touch from Jesus.

00:32:41.398 --> 00:32:49.100
Now, I'm going to pray in tongues and pray perfect prayers out of my spirit.

00:32:49.101 --> 00:33:16.689
I thank You, Holy Spirit, that You move in me and pray perfect prayers that go straight to the throne.

00:33:16.690 --> 00:36:29.838
I'm interceding now over that virus they were talking about, calling forth divine protection over the righteous.

00:36:29.839 --> 00:38:58.274
I'm seeing a wristwatch, a clock that is going backwards, rewinding and giving more time.

00:38:58.275 --> 00:43:13.598
Time is running out. The hand of time is coming to an end for this dispensation. We are getting ready to step into the Millennial Reign.

00:43:13.599 --> 00:43:32.039
When You showed me the wristwatch and Trump, I wondered if we need to lift him up—that his time is not over.

00:43:32.040 --> 00:43:45.814
Father, bring in one final push, waking up the bride and the church.

00:43:45.815 --> 00:44:01.306
We don't look to a man to save this nation; we look to Jesus. It will only be an awakening unto God that will save America.

00:44:01.307 --> 00:44:15.452
I pray a special covering over every individual here, that the plague does not come nigh us.

00:44:15.453 --> 00:44:23.479
No virus in hell can come nigh us. We cover ourselves and our families in the blood.

00:44:23.480 --> 00:44:48.391
We are in the peace that passes all understanding concerning our hearts and families.

00:44:48.392 --> 00:51:24.564
We thank You, Lord, that we're always in the right place at the right time. Thank you for joining me today.

00:51:24.565 --> 00:51:46.047
I know a lot of you have to get back to work, but I wanted to give a little video of prayer so you could jump in the river and get some encouragement on the way to work.

00:51:46.048 --> 00:51:56.645
If you liked it, give it a thumbs up. I'll do more like this if you want to sing or pray more with me.

00:51:56.646 --> 00:52:02.084
It's on my heart. I want to pray more about the thing I just saw: Trump's face and that clock.

00:52:02.085 --> 00:52:12.182
It was a wristwatch moving backwards and then forwards to the 15-minute mark.

00:52:12.183 --> 00:52:41.642
It was a short span of time—a delay, but then it moved back. It's like He's saying time's up; He gave more time, and now the time is up.

00:52:41.643 --> 00:52:54.519
Jesus is coming, folks, and I hope you all are ready. We are going to see a great harvest of souls.

00:52:54.520 --> 00:53:08.159
There is going to be a move of His presence beyond anybody's comprehension. It will be a quick work.

00:53:08.160 --> 00:53:29.439
Then we'll be caught up for the seven-year tribulation to be with Him, and then we'll come back down.

00:53:29.440 --> 00:53:38.660
I want you all to be encouraged today. Yes, there are dark days, but the light is getting lighter.

00:53:38.662 --> 00:53:41.459
You have authority and are seated with Him in the heavenlies.

00:53:41.460 --> 00:53:58.325
You have nothing to fear as a believer bought with the blood of Jesus. To be absent from the body is to be present with the Lord.

00:53:58.326 --> 00:54:05.629
When we die, we go home to see Jesus; we're instantaneously with Him in glory.

00:54:05.630 --> 00:54:13.674
Jesus has a plan for your life to prosper you and be in health, even as your soul prospers.

00:54:13.675 --> 00:54:36.905
There are good days ahead for the believers. If you're new here and never seen me before, God bless you for sticking around.

00:54:36.906 --> 00:54:41.014
I'm going to do more videos like this because the Lord told me to.

00:54:41.015 --> 00:54:54.460
Put a smile on your face and a song in your heart. Jesus loves you so much. God bless you and have a wonderful day. See you next time.

